lyrics:
[Verse]
In a world of darkness, where bullies thrive
There's an army of heroes, ready to revive
Standing together, side by side
We'll spread kindness, let compassion guide

[Chorus]
Paint the town with love, show them we care
Saving souls from bullies, everywhere
With courage as our armor, we will defend
Bringing hope to those whose hearts need to mend
style: song like paint the town red
